Package: CatastRoEus
Title: Interface to the 'INSPIRE' services of 'Catastro de Bizkaia',
    'Catastro de Gipuzkua', 'Catastro de Araba'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jimena", "Salinero", , "jimenasalivega@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Access public spatial data available under the 'INSPIRE'
    directive. Tools for downloading references, buildings and addresses
    of properties on Pais Vasco (Spain).
